  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p><span data-sheets-formula-bar-text-style="font-size:13px;color:#000000;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Arial';font-style:normal;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;">For any trip abroad, it is critical you are insured before you travel and we would also highly recommend that you ensure to take out additional Covid-19 cover. Should you still require insurance, we suggest Campbell Irvine who offer top travel insurance that also offers comprehensive Covid-19 cover. You can find out more and buy online at </span><a href="http://www.campbellirvine.com/InghamsSummer">https://campbellirvinedirect.com/inghamssummer</a></p>]]></shortDescription>
